scenes.description: Opening title card for 'Risu's Isekai Express: Special Performance Delivery'.
Cinematic 3D animation of a large truck traveling through a city and along a tropical beach.
Ayunda Risu greets her viewers from inside the truck's cabin, explaining the concept of her 3D birthday performance.

subtitles.original: RISU'S ISEKAI EXPRESS SPECIAL PERFORMANCE DELIVERY
subtitles.english: RISU'S ISEKAI EXPRESS: SPECIAL PERFORMANCE DELIVERY

subtitles.original: Selamat datang di birthday show Ayunda Risu!
subtitles.english: Welcome to Ayunda Risu's Birthday Show!

subtitles.original: Gimana? Keren nggak, guys? Cia, cia, cia, yak!
subtitles.english: How is it? Cool, right, guys? Cia, cia, cia, yeah!

subtitles.original: Malam ini, guys, kalian diundang untuk ikut dalam pernyanyian sambil naik Risu Isekai Express.
subtitles.english: Tonight, guys, you're invited to join a 'sing-trip' while riding the Risu Isekai Express.
Why do I call it a 'sing-trip'?

subtitles.original: Karena kalian akan diajak pergi ke berbagai macam tempat bersama Risu sambil bernyanyi.
subtitles.english: Because you'll be taken to various places with Risu while singing.

subtitles.original: Jadi kita akan berjalan-jalan, mendaki gunung, melewati pantai, sambil bernyanyi bersama.
subtitles.english: So we'll be traveling around, climbing mountains, passing through beaches, while singing together.

subtitles.original: Terus dapat dilihat juga nih di pojok layar kalian ada hashtag #RiSekaiExpress3D,
subtitles.english: Also, you can see in the corner of your screen there's the hashtag #RiSekaiExpress3D,

subtitles.original: yang bisa kalian pakai untuk membagikan pengalaman perjalanan kalian bersama Risu Isekai Express.
subtitles.english: which you can use to share your travel experience with Risu Isekai Express.
